.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24174_falstaff_hpo_221-270x196.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 274px) 100vw, 274px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="288" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24170_falstaff__hpk_248-288x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="24170_falstaff__hpk_248" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24170_falstaff__hpk_248-288x200.jpg 288w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24170_falstaff__hpk_248-1024x710.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24170_falstaff__hpk_248-270x187.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="192" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24167_falstaff__hpk_234-290x192.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="24167_falstaff__hpk_234" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24167_falstaff__hpk_234-290x192.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24167_falstaff__hpk_234-1024x680.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24167_falstaff__hpk_234-270x179.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="273" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24165_falstaff__hpk_216-273x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="24165_falstaff__hpk_216" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24165_falstaff__hpk_216-273x200.jpg 273w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24165_falstaff__hpk_216-1024x749.jpg 1024w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24165_falstaff__hpk_216-270x197.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 273px) 100vw, 273px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="188" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/24164_falstaff__hpk_89-290x188.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="24164_falstaff__hpk_89" srcset=